money for the county's bare coffers has netted some unusual
donations, including trout worms and batch of silver dental
fillings, but not much cash.
   ``I started Tuesday taking up a radio appeal, so far having
raised $35.18,'' said Mark Brueckmann of radio station WSBS in Great
Barrington.
