<DATELINE>BRADENTON, Fla. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Gregg Allman and his band have been
playing at an abandoned shopping center in this Gulf Coast community
to prepare for a six-week reunion tour marking their 20th
anniversary.
   The Allman Brothers Band, with four original members and three
newcomers, plan primarily outdoor concerts to mark the founding of
the rock group in 1969. The band went on to record ``Statesboro
Blues'' and ``Whipping Post.''
